<br>
If our class is going to be the beneficiary of changes, do you want them focused more on our being able to go toe to toe with other people or more on helping our groups be more effective through chants?</FONT><br><br><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2><B>Results (total votes = 51):</B></FONT><table bgcolor=#FFFFFF border=0 cellpadding=3 cellspacing=0 width="75%"><tbody><tr><td bgcolor="#000000" colspan=3 height=1></tr><TR BGCOLOR=#E0E0E0><TD NOWRAP><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2>Skalds are primarily a support class</FONT>&nbsp</td><td height><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2>11&nbsp;/&nbsp;21.6%</FONT>&nbsp</td><td><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/bar.gif width=64 height=10 hspace=3>&nbsp;</td></tr><tr><td bgcolor="#000000" colspan=3 height=1></tr><TR BGCOLOR=#E0E0E0><TD NOWRAP><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2>Skalds are primarily a melee class</FONT>&nbsp</td><td height><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2>40&nbsp;/&nbsp;78.4%</FONT>&nbsp</td><td><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/bar.gif width=235 height=10 hspace=3>&nbsp;</td></tr><tr><td bgcolor="#000000" colspan=3 height=1></tr></tbody></table><a href=http://pub36.ezboard.com/fteamskaldfrm1.showMessage?topicID=656.topic><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2>Vote Now</FONT></a> &nbsp <p>Gotter Dammerung - 50 skald<br />
