<br>
<blockquote style="padding-left:0.5em; margin-left:0; margin-right:0; margin-top:0; margin-bottom:0; border-left:solid 2">Unlike some classes, Skalds are not intended to hang out in the back of a fight, out of harm's way.  It's more reasonable to expect a Skald to be in the thick of battle, likely meleeing and/or interrupting healers and casters.</blockquote><br>
<br>
So there you have it finally.  Let's focus on that as our goal and work from that mindset.<br>
<br>
Rosey<br>
